A cozy winter scene in Studio Ghibli style featuring a cheerful penguin wearing an orange and maroon cycling jersey, sitting contentedly next to a stylish backpack under a softly glowing Christmas tree. The room is warmly lit with gentle golden light from paper lanterns, snowflakes drifting past a frosted window. The penguin has a satisfied, peaceful expression. Wrapped gifts in warm earth tones surround the scene, with delicate watercolor textures and the signature soft, dreamy atmosphere of Japanese animation. Pine branches with small ornaments frame the edges of the image.
